@startuml
title YPS CSV Import & 7AM Scheduler (Simplified View)

hide footbox
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor ImportService as IMP
participant YPS_FileServer as YFS
participant "SaleService" as SS
note right of IMP
For each transaction row:
IMP delegates the real processing to SaleService
end note
database import_record as IR
note right of IR
For import info , session status ,transaction status
accestime,importstatus,activeSessionCount,failedtx,filename,totaltx,isEmailSent,remark
end note
database import_session as IS
note right of IS
must column
session_id,store_id
end note
database CDSG_ESERVICEHEADERTABLE as SH
database SaleTransaction as ST
database yps_integration as YPS
note right of YPS
add fromOnline column(true/false)
api may true but other may false
end note
database workshift as WT

actor "7amScheduler" as SCH
participant MailService as MAIL
participant MailConfig as MC

== IMPORT PROCESS ==

IMP -> YFS: Fetch CSV File
YFS --> IMP: Return CSV Data

note right of IMP
CSV may contain:
- Multiple stores
- Multiple transactions per store
Example:
3 stores x 3 transactions each
end note

IMP -> IR: Insert import_record\n(status=IN_PROGRESS,\nactiveSession=0,\nfailedCount=0,\nisEmailSent=false)

note right of IMP
For each store:
1 Sale Header created
1 Import Session created
activeSessionCount++
end note

IMP -> SH: Create Sale Header
SH --> IMP: saleHeaderId

IMP -> IS: Insert Import Session (ACTIVE)
IS --> IMP: OK

IMP -> IR: Update activeSessionCount +1

note right of IMP
For each transaction row:
- Insert SaleTransaction
- Try processing
end note

IMP -> SS: processSaleTransaction ()

alt Success
    SS -> ST: Store sale info
    SS-->IMP:success
else Failed
    SS -> YPS: Insert/Update failed record\n(status=FAIL, source=MANUAL)
    SS-->IMP:failed
    IMP -> IR: Update failedCount +1
end

IMP -> IR: Update status=COMPLETED

== 7AM SHIFT CHECK ==

SCH -> IR: Find import_record where activeSessionCount > 0

note right of SCH
For each active session:
Check if any SaleTransaction
status = PROCESS
end note

SCH -> ST: Check status=PROCESS

alt PROCESS found
    SCH -> WT: Close Workshift
    SCH -> IS: Update session status=CLOSED
    SCH -> IR: Decrease activeSessionCount
else No PROCESS
    note right: No action needed
end

== 7AM FAILED EMAIL CHECK ==

SCH -> IR: Find failedCount > 0 AND isEmailSent=false

note right of SCH
Determine date range:
from = lastEmailSentAt or importStartAt
to = now
end note

SCH -> YPS: Fetch failed records\n(status=FAIL, source=MANUAL)

alt Fail records exist
    SCH -> MAIL: Send failure report
    MAIL -> MC: Load SMTP config
    MAIL --> SCH: Email sent
    SCH -> IR: Update isEmailSent=true
else No failed record
    note right: No email sent
end

@enduml
